ction\nexcept RemoteDisconnected as e:\n    # handle the exception, e.g., by retrying the connection or logging the error\n    print(f\"Error: {e}\")\n```\n\nAs for the travel planning, I can provide you with a revised itinerary based on your original request. Here is a 2-day itinerary for a trip to Goa:\n\n**Day 1:**\n\n* **Morning (9:00 am - 12:00 pm):** Start your day with a delicious breakfast at a local caf\u00e9 in Panjim, the capital city of Goa. Visit the **Se Cathedral** (entry fee: 10 INR) and **Basilica of Bom Jesus** (entry fee: free), two of the most famous churches in Goa.\n* **Afternoon (12:00 pm - 4:00 pm):** Head to **Miramar Beach** (entry fee: free) for some relaxation and sunbathing. You can also try water sports like parasailing or jet-skiing (approx. cost: 500-1000 INR per person).\n* **Evening (4:00 pm - 8:00 pm):** Visit the **Dona Paula** viewpoint (entry fee: free) to watch the sunset. Later, head to **Candolim Beach** (entry fee: free) for a stroll and dinner at one of the many restaurants.\n\n**Day 2:**\n\n* **Morning (9:00 am - 12:00 pm):** Visit the **Fort Aguada** (entry fee: 50 INR) and explore the historic fort. Take a short walk to the **Aguada Beach** (entry fee: free) for some relaxation.\n* **Afternoon (12:00 pm - 4:00 pm):** Head to **Calangute Beach** (entry fee: free) for some water sports and activities. You can also try a **Dolphin-watching tour** (approx. cost: 1000-1500 INR per person).\n* **Evening (4:00 pm - 8:00 pm):** Visit the **Baga Beach** (entry fee: free) for a lively atmosphere and dinner at one of the many restaurants.\n\n**Hotel Suggestions:**\n\n* **Budget:** Hotel Palacio De Goa (approx. cost: 2,500 INR per night)\n* **Mid-range:** Lemon Tree Hotel (approx. cost: 4,500 INR per night)\n* **Luxury:** The Leela Goa (approx. cost: 10,000 INR per night)\n\n**Budget Breakdown:**\n\n* **Accommodation (2 nights):**\n\t+ Budget: 5,000 INR (2,500 INR per night)\n\t+ Mid-range: 9,000 INR (4,500 INR per night)\n\t+ Luxury: 20,000 INR (10,000 INR per night)\n* **Food (2 days):** 8,000 INR (approx. 4,000 INR per day for meals and snacks)\n* **Transportation (2 days):** 2,000 INR (approx. 1,000 INR per day for taxi or rental car)\n* **Attraction entry fees:** 100 INR (approx. 50 INR per person for all attractions)\n* **Water sports and activities:** 2,000 INR (approx. 1,000 INR per person for parasailing, jet-skiing, and dolphin-watching tour)\n* **Total estimated trip cost:** 27,100 INR (budget), 30,100 INR (mid-range), 41,100 INR (luxury)\n\nI hope this revised itinerary meets your requirements. Let me know if you have any further questions or need any additional assistance."}, {"role": "assistant", "tool_calls": [{"id": "9vtrwkh6q", "function": {"arguments": "{\"query\":\"Goa tourist spots\"}", "name": "tavily_tool"}, "type": "function"}, {"id": "y9zq2q51s", "function": {"arguments": "{\"query\":\"Se Cathedral entry fee\"}", "name": "tavily_tool"}, "type": "function"}, {"id": "2aq7x31r8", "function": {"arguments": "{\"query\":\"Basilica of Bom Jesus entry fee\"}", "name": "tavily_tool"}, "type": "function"}, {"id": "pjbxqan1q", "function": {"arguments": "{\"query\":\"Miramar Beach activities\"}", "name": "tavily_tool"}, "type": "function"}, {"id": "xsysq87zr", "function": {"arguments": "{\"query\":\"Dona Paula viewpoint sunset time\"}", "name": "tavily_tool"}, "type": "function"}, {"id": "3m1gxvebv", "function": {"arguments": "{\"query\":\"Candolim Beach restaurants\"}", "name": "tavily_tool"}, "type": "function"}, {"id": "d31gy2wxf", "function": {"arguments": "{\"query\":\"Fort Aguada entry fee\"}", "name": "tavily_tool"}, "type": "function"}, {"id": "rh7nn3fyy", "function": {"arguments": "{\"query\":\"Aguada Beach activities\"}", "name": "tavily_tool"}, "type": "function"}, {"id": "zqxcj32bd", "function": {"arguments": "{\"query\":\"Calangute Beach water sports\"}", "name": "tavily_tool"}, "type": "function"}, {"id": "q1dwqjk97", "function": {"arguments": "{\"query\":\"Baga Beach