 or need any additional assistance.\\n\\nHere are the hotel details:\\n\\n* **Regenta Inn Palacio De Goa:**\\n\\t+ Address: Panjim, Goa\\n\\t+ Check-in: 1:00 PM\\n\\t+ Check-out: 11:00 AM\\n\\t+ Room types: Standard, Deluxe, Premium\\n\\t+ Amenities: Free Wi-Fi, outdoor swimming pool, restaurant, bar\\n* **Lemon Tree Hotel:**\\n\\t+ Address: Candolim, Goa\\n\\t+ Check-in: 3:00 PM\\n\\t+ Check-out: 12:00 PM\\n\\t+ Room types: Deluxe, Executive, Suite\\n\\t+ Amenities: Free Wi-Fi, outdoor swimming pool, restaurant, bar\\n* **The Leela Goa:**\\n\\t+ Address: Cavelossim, Goa\\n\\t+ Check-in: 3:00 PM\\n\\t+ Check-out: 12:00 PM\\n\\t+ Room types: Standard, Deluxe, Suite\\n\\t+ Amenities: Free Wi-Fi, outdoor swimming pool, private beach, tennis courts, spa\\n\\nPlease note that the prices and availability may vary depending on the season and availability. I recommend checking with the hotels directly for the most up-to-date information.\\n\\nHere is a summary of the hotel prices:\\n\\n* **Regenta Inn Palacio De Goa:**\\n\\t+ Standard Room: 2,500 INR per night\\n\\t+ Deluxe Room: 3,500 INR per night\\n\\t+ Premium Room: 4,500 INR per night\\n* **Lemon Tree Hotel:**\\n\\t+ Deluxe Room: 4,500 INR per night\\n\\t+ Executive Room: 5,500 INR per night\\n\\t+ Suite: 7,000 INR per night\\n* **The Leela Goa:**\\n\\t+ Standard Room: 10,000 INR per night\\n\\t+ Deluxe Room: 12,000 INR per night\\n\\t+ Suite: 15,000 INR per night\\n\\nI hope this information helps you plan your trip to Goa. Let me know if you have any further questions or need any additional assistance.\",\"type\":\"TextMessage\"},\"inner_messages\":[]},\"name\":\"Travel_Planner\"}", "sender": "Travel_Planner_3e642f2a-4757-4d43-9ba9-b18e90e0f90b/3e642f2a-4757-4d43-9ba9-b18e90e0f90b", "receiver": null, "kind": "MessageKind.PUBLISH", "delivery_stage": "DeliveryStage.DELIVER", "type": "Message"}
